00:07:28.480 --> 00:07:34.380
paintings is sold for €1,000, then you, the artist, will get €500.

00:07:34.940 --> 00:07:40.190
Let’s say that your fame continues to grow, and instead of selling

00:07:40.190 --> 00:07:46.070
paintings for a thousand euros, you can now sell them for 50,000 euros.

00:07:46.977 --> 00:07:49.367
A gallery would still want its commission.

00:07:49.707 --> 00:07:57.315
It might be a little bit less than 50% now, but let’s say you negotiated well you might get €30,000.

00:07:58.572 --> 00:08:02.237
Your early fans, people who believed in you from the

00:08:02.237 --> 00:08:06.777
