You decide to offer a limited edition of 100 digital copies of your favourite painting.

00:09:28.449 --> 00:09:32.679
They are all slightly different, perhaps they use slightly different

00:09:32.729 --> 00:09:37.169
colours, or perhaps they are numbered, like limited edition prints.

00:09:37.829 --> 00:09:41.189
You offer these for sale directly to your fans.

00:09:41.349 --> 00:09:43.699
