00:09:44.299 --> 00:09:49.899
Perhaps you sell it through a marketplace, which might take 15% or

00:09:49.899 --> 00:09:54.489
something like that, but you get to keep the majority of the sale price.

00:09:55.379 --> 00:10:01.089
